<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1101,1188]" pageId="4" pageNumber="14">
This new species is characterized by its large size (ca. 
<quantity box="[775,861,1101,1124]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3" pageId="4" pageNumber="14" unit="cm" value="130.0">130 cm</quantity>
), its elongate peduncle and dense globose to ovoid inflorescence, that is in general not very colourful, with relatively large floral bracts (3.5 × 2.0 cm), flowers (
<quantity box="[1354,1429,1133,1156]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" pageId="4" pageNumber="14" unit="cm" value="4.5">4.5 cm</quantity>
) and sepals (27 × 9.5–11.0 mm).
</paragraph>
